fsuite (1.8.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * feat(fread): add budgeted file reading tool with head/tail, ranges,
    around-line, around-pattern, stdin path mode, and unified-diff mode
  * feat(fread): add binary detection, token estimation, next_hint, and
    line-numbered JSON/pretty/paths output for agent-friendly reading
  * fix(fread): make telemetry timestamps portable on macOS/BSD with
    fallback millisecond clock path
  * tests: add dedicated fread suite and wire into master runner
  * packaging: install fread in Debian package
  * docs: promote suite to six tools and document fread in README
  * release: unify all tool versions at 1.8.0

