fsuite (1.7.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Unified version bump: all tools now 1.7.0
  * fix(ftree): recon path identity at depth > 1 — positional rel_path, JSON path field
  * fix(ftree): timeout detection via structured output protocol (subshell var fix)
  * fix(ftree): total_size_bytes preserves -1 sentinel for unknown sizes
  * fix(telemetry): run_id-based dedup replaces timestamp-based UNIQUE constraint
  * fix(telemetry): atomic DB migration with .bail on + BEGIN IMMEDIATE
  * fix(telemetry): legacy JSONL import backfills run_id
  * fix(fsearch): bounded memory — head -n before mapfile + || true guards
  * fix(fcontent): -q exit code 1 on no match (matches README contract)
  * fix(fmetrics-predict): version aligned to suite
  * fsearch: add include/exclude filtering (-I/-x) with wildcard matching (PR #6)
  * fcontent: path deduplication in output (PR #5)
  * New tests: 281 total across 6 suites, migration atomicity test

