fsuite (1.6.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * fix(fcontent): add missing exit 0 in pretty output mode (PR #5, Cwilliams333)
  * feat(fcontent): dedupe repeated file paths in output — show full path on
    first occurrence, basename-only for subsequent same-file matches
  * Uses declare -A associative array for robust non-contiguous dedup
  * Regex fix: [^:]+ instead of greedy .+ for reliable path:line:content parsing
  * fsearch: add production-grade path filtering via repeatable --include/-I and --exclude/-x
  * fsearch: add support for wildcard matching when filter pattern contains *, ?, or [] and order-preserving filtering
  * fsearch: include include/exclude patterns in telemetry flags field

