fsuite (1.6.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Hardening patch: LC_ALL=C locale pinning for consistent grep behavior
  * .h header heuristic: detect C++ constructs before defaulting to C
  * json_escape rewrite: sed → perl for full control char handling
  * O(n²) string concat → temp file streaming for large symbol sets
  * Safety: -- before filenames in all grep calls
  * Java: package-private method detection (optional access modifier)
  * Missing-value checks for all option flags
  * Paths output respects --max-symbols cap
  * Test robustness: canonical JSON booleans, argv passing, crash reporting
  * docs: Episode 1 — The Fourth Drone (fmap origin story)

